schools.name: Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr. Early College

data.description:
This beautiful two bedroom, two bathroom home is now available for sale in the desirable Green Valley Ranch neighborhood. 

The house features an open concept floor plan with large windows that bring in plenty of natural light. The kitchen boasts a large island, stainless steel appliances, and all appliances are included in the sale. The home also features a balcony, perfect for relaxing with a morning cup of coffee or an evening glass of wine.

The property is eligible for FHA financing, and the assumable loan makes the property even more attractive.

This is a fantastic opportunity to own a great home in a desirable neighborhood. With two bedrooms, two bathrooms, and all the features this house has to offer, you won't want to miss out. Don't wait, contact us today to schedule a viewing and make this house your home.
